{"tid":1553403,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[反攻social media] 將會舉行一場最大型既國際文宣運動","createTime":"2019-09-08T15:04:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T20:06:41.000Z","uid":281955,"like":90,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":97,"replies":[{"pid":"951a702d486db58bdd752ab2fcc0fd659727d0b4","tid":1553403,"uid":281955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:04:29.000Z","msg":"各位，我地係國際文宣株式會社，上一個post 講到我地要改變文宣策略要將文宣影片加入故事性同情感元素令外國人覺得香港抗爭唔再係停留係新聞層面，要拉攏一眾外國左膠同和理非人，詳見當年time magazine 點用一張相引起［welcome refugees] 運動。<br />\n<br />\n呢場運動我地會將製成品係唔同社交媒體到落廣告，反攻social media贏輿論，而家我地製片組同graphic 組已經成立，但嚴重缺人，要打贏場文宣戰，我地要大量各路人仕加入<br />\n<br />\n徵求：<br />\n剪片製片人仕<br />\nGraphic design人仕<br />\nMarketing agency (嚴重缺人，要你地幫手聯絡各大媒體落廣告）<br />\n<br />\n假如呢次成功，會有薄酬比返你地<br />\n<br />\nTg channel: <a href=\"http://t.me/internationalforhk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Finternationalforhk&d=h%2B0F1AfFk4MBaO73S6qK%2BoeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=847fa400\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/internationalforhk</a><br />\n<br />\nDM: <a href=\"https://t.me/tylerdurdennnnn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftylerdurdennnnn&d=h%2B0F1AfFk4MBaO73S6qK%2BoeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=5e932682\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/tylerdurdennnnn</a><br />\n<br />\n上一個post<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1544695\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1544695</a>"},{"pid":"a74f8cba351a941c8e2383f12dc387ccfd87fe3a","tid":1553403,"uid":8165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:06:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2dfd840ef21b269a3e5c8472a6054a4efcb648bc","tid":1553403,"uid":281955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:09:12.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1b4f90cb8e2be4c04f74583754024cb4f424352","tid":1553403,"uid":187950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:10:03.000Z","msg":"推"